net.myorb.math.primenumbers

Interface FactorCollection


  • public interface FactorCollection
    the functionality required to represent a set of factors making up a value. the factorization is built as a collection of prime^exponent pairs which multiplied together make the value. the methods of this interface allow queries of the primes and their exponents.
    Author:
    Michael Druckman
